                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 5.648,
                                "byte_start": 105472,
                                "byte_stop": 128146,
                                "text": "This is a ERISA pension case which means it\u0027s pretty complicated."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 5.648,
                                "stop": 19.099,
                                "byte_start": 128146,
                                "byte_stop": 181959,
                                "text": "But in the case, petitioner was a company called CIGNA runs a pension plan for its employees and the plan is governed by ERISA, the Employment Retirement Security Act of 18 -- 1974."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 19.099,
                                "stop": 28.503,
                                "byte_start": 181959,
                                "byte_stop": 219575,
                                "text": "Now under ERISA, participants in a pension plan are entitled to get periodic summaries of their benefits and obligations."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 28.503,
                                "stop": 42.67,
                                "byte_start": 219575,
                                "byte_stop": 276208,
                                "text": "In 1997, CIGNA decided to change its pension plan and it sent notices to the plan participants but the notices omitted certain key details about reductions of the rate that employees would accrue benefits in the future."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 42.67,
                                "stop": 52.984,
                                "byte_start": 276208,
                                "byte_stop": 317482,
                                "text": "And in particular, it -- they -- CIGNA did not tell its employees that -- because of a mathematical core of a certain kind, the way in which the -- they were going to calculate those benefits."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 52.984,
                                "stop": 57.902,
                                "byte_start": 317482,
                                "byte_stop": 337126,
                                "text": "Those employees could work many years without accruing any additional benefits."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 57.902,
                                "stop": 63.474,
                                "byte_start": 337126,
                                "byte_stop": 359382,
                                "text": "After the bench trial, the District Court found that CIGNA\u0027s disclosures violated ERISA."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 63.474,
                                "stop": 67.475,
                                "byte_start": 359382,
                                "byte_stop": 375474,
                                "text": "So, there\u0027s a violation, but what\u0027s the remedy?"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 67.475,
                                "stop": 76.303,
                                "byte_start": 375474,
                                "byte_stop": 410687,
                                "text": "CIGNA claimed that there is no remedy unless the participants proved that they relied upon the misstatements to their detriment."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 76.303,
                                "stop": 79.039,
                                "byte_start": 410687,
                                "byte_stop": 421658,
                                "text": "The District Court found there could be a remedy."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 79.039,
                                "stop": 98.387,
                                "byte_start": 421658,
                                "byte_stop": 499085,
                                "text": "If the false disclosures resulted in likely harm to the plan participants and it said, \u0022Well, the participants here can get -- recover the benefits because -- under a remedy provision, 502(a)(1)(B)\u0022, which I\u0027m going to call remedy prong one."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 98.387,
                                "stop": 106.47,
                                "byte_start": 499085,
                                "byte_stop": 531372,
                                "text": "That prong one permits the participant, \u201cto recover benefits due to him under the terms of the plan.\u201d"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 106.47,
                                "stop": 110.215,
                                "byte_start": 531372,
                                "byte_stop": 546419,
                                "text": "So, the Second Circuit affirmed to get the remedy."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 110.215,
                                "stop": 115.999,
                                "byte_start": 546419,
                                "byte_stop": 569511,
                                "text": "But we granted cert to determine what standard of harm the participants have to satisfy."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 115.999,
                                "stop": 119.423,
                                "byte_start": 569511,
                                "byte_stop": 583199,
                                "text": "Is it as the District Court thought likely harm?"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 119.423,
                                "stop": 123.949,
                                "byte_start": 583199,
                                "byte_stop": 601276,
                                "text": "Or is it as CIGNA said reliance to ones detriment?"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 123.949,
                                "stop": 133.168,
                                "byte_start": 601276,
                                "byte_stop": 638161,
                                "text": "But we first found that we have to consider whether the District Court should have treated the summary benefit descriptions under remedy prong one."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 133.168,
                                "stop": 137.514,
                                "byte_start": 638161,
                                "byte_stop": 655611,
                                "text": "Was this whole thing benefits due under the terms of the plan?"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 137.514,
                                "stop": 139.334,
                                "byte_start": 655611,
                                "byte_stop": 662821,
                                "text": "Well, so now what do we hold?"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 139.334,
                                "stop": 146.077,
                                "byte_start": 662821,
                                "byte_stop": 689883,
                                "text": "Well, in a sense we hold that that prong one, benefits due under the plan in this case is the wrong prong."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 146.077,
                                "stop": 149.314,
                                "byte_start": 689883,
                                "byte_stop": 702736,
                                "text": "The District Court\u0027s remedy consisted of two steps."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 149.314,
                                "stop": 154.404,
                                "byte_start": 702736,
                                "byte_stop": 723111,
                                "text": "The first step was to reform the terms of the plan to comport with the summary documents."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 154.404,
                                "stop": 159.434,
                                "byte_start": 723111,
                                "byte_stop": 743278,
                                "text": "The second was to make CIGNA enforce the plan as it was rewritten."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 159.434,
                                "stop": 169.912,
                                "byte_start": 743278,
                                "byte_stop": 785178,
                                "text": "Now that second step is certainly part of enforcing the plan benefits but we don\u0027t see how changing the plan can be part of -- in giving them the benefits due under the plan."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 169.912,
                                "stop": 173.72,
                                "byte_start": 785178,
                                "byte_stop": 800434,
                                "text": "So where does the District Court get the authority to do that?"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 173.72,
                                "stop": 182.673,
                                "byte_start": 800434,
                                "byte_stop": 836169,
                                "text": "Well, the failure of the District Court to bring us remedy within prong one does not mean that the participants are necessarily out of luck."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 182.673,
                                "stop": 198.281,
                                "byte_start": 836169,
                                "byte_stop": 898654,
                                "text": "That\u0027s because there\u0027s another remedial provision, 502(a)(3) called prong two and that permits the participants to obtain, \u201cother appropriate equitable relief to redress ERISA violations.\u201d"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 198.281,
                                "stop": 203.014,
                                "byte_start": 898654,
                                "byte_stop": 917567,
                                "text": "The District Court thought that that relief was unavailable but we disagree."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 203.014,
                                "stop": 215.585,
                                "byte_start": 917567,
                                "byte_stop": 967826,
                                "text": "Under one of our earlier cases called Mertens, the phrase appropriate equitable relief refers to those categories of relief that before the merger of law and equity were typically available in equity."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 215.585,
                                "stop": 224.923,
                                "byte_start": 967826,
                                "byte_stop": 1005234,
                                "text": "And so we looked it up and we found that there are at least three remedies here from equity, consistent with what the District Court did."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 224.923,
                                "stop": 227.18,
                                "byte_start": 1005234,
                                "byte_stop": 1014220,
                                "text": "It might satisfy the standard."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 227.18,
                                "stop": 233.227,
                                "byte_start": 1014220,
                                "byte_stop": 1038461,
                                "text": "Courts in equity use to reform an instrument to reflect the parties\u0027 mutual intent."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 233.227,
                                "stop": 238.629,
                                "byte_start": 1038461,
                                "byte_stop": 1060091,
                                "text": "They used to be able to stop a party from benefiting from its factor misrepresentations."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 238.629,
                                "stop": 245.515,
                                "byte_start": 1060091,
                                "byte_stop": 1087572,
                                "text": "And they used to be able to surcharge awarding money damages against the trustee for a breach of his duty."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 245.515,
                                "stop": 260.257,
                                "byte_start": 1087572,
                                "byte_stop": 1146504,
                                "text": "We\u0027ll leave it to the District Court to determine which if any of these remedies is appropriate in light of the facts of this case and that leaves us with the question we initially agreed to decide, whether showing of likely harm is sufficient under ERISA."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 260.257,
                                "stop": 272.56,
                                "byte_start": 1146504,
                                "byte_stop": 1195719,
                                "text": "For purposes of this prong two, we conclude that the standard of prejudice that applies must be the standard -- the same standard that would\u0027ve applied to the particular (Inaudible) -- equitable remedy that\u0027s imposed."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 272.56,
                                "stop": 282.485,
                                "byte_start": 1195719,
                                "byte_stop": 1235425,
                                "text": "For example, detrimental reliance would\u0027ve been and it would be required for relief based on the equitable remedy of the estoppel as it used to be in the Court of equity."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 282.485,
                                "stop": 296.007,
                                "byte_start": 1235425,
                                "byte_stop": 1289550,
                                "text": "But, its only a showing of actual harm would\u0027ve been necessary for relief based on the equitable remedy of surcharge for these reasons and those given at even greater length."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 296.007,
                                "stop": 302.942,
                                "byte_start": 1289550,
                                "byte_stop": 1317345,
                                "text": "In our opinion filed today, we vacate the judgment of the Second Circuit and we remand for further proceeds."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 302.942,
                                "stop": 308.618,
                                "byte_start": 1317345,
                                "byte_stop": 1340019,
                                "text": "Justice Scalia has filed an opinion concurring in the judgment in which Justice Thomas joins."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 308.618,
                                "stop": 312.242,
                                "byte_start": 1340019,
                                "byte_stop": 0,
                                "text": "Justice Sotomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this case."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
